  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">In this paper, by using Lorentzian matrix multiplication, L-Tangent operator is obtained in Lorentzian space. The L-Tangent operators related with planar, spherical and spatial motion are computed via special matrix groups. L-Tangent operators are related to vectors. Some illustrative examples for applications of L-Tangent operators are also presented.</subfield>
